text: Zoë Carroll Chao (born September 19, 1985) is an American actress and screenwriter. She is known for her roles as Isobel in Strangers, Zoë in The Afterparty and Nina Mazursky in Creature Commandos. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from Providence, Rhode Island Category:Writers from Providence, Rhode Island Category:American screenwriters
